Bowtie: an Ultrafast, Lightweight Short Read Aligner

Bowtie NEWS
===========

   The first release of the Bowtie is now available for download.
Version 1.0.0 is the first version to be released under the OSI
Artistic License (see `COPYING') and freely available to the public
for download.  The Bowtie project is still in its early development
stages, and everyone interested in improving this project is strongly
encouraged to contact us. See the project website for more details.

Version Release History
=======================

Version 1.0.0 - August 2008

     * First official release of the Bowtie distribution.
